&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Accurate stage progression&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Consistent definitions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reliable funnel and conversion reporting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with regional marketing teams to drive alignment on shared definitions and templates&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify manual, repetitive workflows and work with Business Systems to design and enable scalable automation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage Marketo system changes and coordinate with Business Systems&lt;/li&gt;
